trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A> method just before adding a control to a Web Parts zone.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>evento é originado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A>método antes de adicionar um controlo a uma zona de peças Web.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>

trans-unit.source: This event provides an opportunity to cancel the process before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: Este evento fornece uma oportunidade para cancelar o processo antes de terminar.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded> event is called after a control has been added to a Web Parts zone.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>evento for chamado depois de um controlo foi adicionado a uma zona de peças Web.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartAddingEventArgs class contains information that can be used within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding> event.
trans-unit.target: A classe de WebPartAddingEventArgs contém informações que podem ser utilizadas dentro de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>eventos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts control that is being added and the zone it is being added to.
trans-unit.target: Fornece acesso para o controlo de peças Web que está a ser adicionado e está a ser adicionado à zona.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartAddingEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartAddingEventArgs"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> (or server or user control) to be added to a Web page or opened on a page.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> (ou controlo de utilizador ou servidor) para ser adicionado a uma página Web ou abrir numa página.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that `webPart` is being added to.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> que `webPart` está a ser adicionado ao.

trans-unit.source: An integer that represents the ordinal position that `webPart` occupies in `zone`, relative to other controls in `zone`.
trans-unit.target: Um número inteiro que representa a ordinal da posição que `webPart` ocupar no `zone`relativos a outros controlos `zone`.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Web Parts zone that the Web Parts control is being added to.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a que o controlo de peças Web está a ser adicionado à zona de peças Web.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that the Web Parts control is being added to.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> que o controlo de peças Web está a ser adicionado ao.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the index position of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control within its zone.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a posição de índice de uma <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controlo dentro do respetivo zona.

trans-unit.source: The ZoneIndex property indicates the numerical order (or ordinal position) within the zone for the Web Parts control being added in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded> event.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade ZoneIndex indica o número de ordem numérica (ou posição ordinal) na zona para o controlo de peças Web a serem adicionado no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>eventos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this property to track and manage its collection of Web Parts controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controlo utiliza esta propriedade para controlar e gerir a sua coleção de controlos de peças Web numa página Web.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The value of the ZoneIndex property for a control might not equal the index value for the same control within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > O valor da propriedade ZoneIndex para um controlo poderá não ser igual um valor de índice para o controlo dentro do mesmo a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A>coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The numerical order of a control within its zone.
trans-unit.target: A ordem numérica de um controlo dentro do respetivo zona.

trans-unit.source: The first control in a zone has an index value of zero.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro controlo numa zona tem um valor de índice de zero.
